Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.26,0:01:13.85,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.04,0:01:19.03,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Hope to be with you even after rebirth.....Rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:26.17,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今日が過去に変わる事で、明日が近づいて。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:33.42,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}そんな当たり前の事に　心は傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:37.50,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}あの日見た『世界』を　もう一度作ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:42.99,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}叶う時が　いつか来るなら　もう何もいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:50.78,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}まるで可能性が無いと　誰に揶揄されても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:55.64,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}次の君に逢える日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:59.59,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}繰り返し　巡る運命が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:02.95,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}たとえ　どんな道でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:06.58,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}決して　決して　諦めない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:10.35,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}『あした、またね。』　その『未来』を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:14.14,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}いつまでも失くさないように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:17.69,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}終わりのない始まり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:23.07,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今、君と夢見たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:27.82,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}繋いだ手を　離さないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:31.00,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:34.67,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Hope to be with you even after rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.88,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change.
